{"tid":1234930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 你知唔知你自己做啲咩","createTime":"2019-06-17T04:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:05:16.000Z","uid":236709,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3498355a23a1b1999ad65a505f6e0142d704455b","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:35:44.000Z","msg":"6月9號6月12號6月16號<br />\n呢幾日都經過咗<br />\n但所有嘅氣力犧牲都好似換唔到任何嘢<br />\n政府似乎想一拖再拖<br />\n拖低我哋嘅士氣<br />\n見人少就通過<br />\n呢樣大家都心裏明白<br />\n但今日我想講嘅唔係呢件事<br />\n<br />\n而家我想講我哋應該點樣走落去<br />\n站係一個中共嘅立場睇<br />\n一個地方有200萬人上街反對佢嘅政權<br />\n係一件非常危險嘅事<br />\n真係得到 絕對嘅 控制權的話<br />\n清算 嘅斧頭 就已經係香港人頸上<br />\n<br />\n一百萬人已經非常之危險<br />\n200萬人已經係一個城市嘅作反<br />\n如果你喺reddit見過啲留言的話<br />\n你見佢哋講嘅全部都同64 拉埋一齊講<br />\n或者 我哋身為香港人未必會諗到咁偏<br />\n但當局者迷<br />\n或者佢哋冇講錯 我哋已經落中共面落得太多<br />\n<br />\n你可以咁講<br />\n香港 其實喺呢一刻開始<br />\n已經冇咗退路<br />\n送中條例過咗 清算係一定會存在<br />\n但就算送中條例撤回 清算嘅可能 依然存在<br />\n究竟我哋要點樣 先可以完全避免 清算?<br />\n我希望大家可以藉 政府故意製造嘅寧靜<br />\n好好諗一下<br />\n我哋香港要如何走落去 如何先可以係未來安寢<br />\n英文有一句諺語<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Do or die</span><br />\n或者呢句真係 好徹合我哋嘅 狀況<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Do</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Die</span>"},{"pid":"6fa800281a3a4d282f14507d82bcd80f2c0af860","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34077aec89e4f44269238f357f4e5d8036502b3c","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2737c98c712370a4fe7cccbeaf9d01ec61c9ea13","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e000b5e65a58399bb28e4e3259ae1248b0b2a53c","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a25a769c05f51d7ac596eeb8bbd6d87849d691","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c559c71c068855b3b9880b8054e6afb8f9eeac","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf673120012778433e94d7a42da3ce19bff81aa5","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"OO"},{"pid":"462049c08402baf4336df130949c03ea614c76eb","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:51:02.000Z","msg":"Icon icon"},{"pid":"a56f9709140036ff77296d4b52e4d0ba32811be8","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffa96f6b47a5d12af53307f462c85fdff447fce","tid":1234930,"uid":236709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:54:52.000Z","msg":"唉 唉"},{"pid":"bcc53412159b379d26924d410fb7c2a849ea737b","tid":1234930,"uid":2367